HEADWORD: Perhaps
<hw>Per*haps"</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r*h⟦acr⟧ps")</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Per</ets> + <ets>hap</ets> chance.]</ety> <def>Possibly; by
chance; peradventure; perchance; it may be.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And pray God, if <qex>perhaps</qex> the thought of thine heart may
be forgiven thee.</q> <rj><qau>Acts viii. 22.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

